00/extras/7be62a1087678210a6f09447dfd8712f.webp?t=1631653168\" width=32 height=32 /></span> Built on a fresh new fighting game framework made from scratch in Unity<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739200/extras/c2129bf0178ecfc7a5e7ff9300d68d9d.webp?t=1631653168\" width=32 height=32 /></span> Many of the advanced techniques you know and love from anime fighters",
